headline.main: Tennis: Former Cricketer Barty Puts Runs on the Board in Return
headline.print_headline: Tennis: Former Cricketer Barty Puts Runs on the Board in Return

lead_paragraph: The relentless grind of the professional tennis tour proved too much for Australia's Ashleigh Barty during her teenage years but a break from the game to play cricket appears to be paying some pretty big dividends.
